comments.comment: Additional Assessment 1: DV $500.00 THE DEFENDANT IS ORDERED TO PERFORM 5 DAYS BEACH CLEAN-UP. DEFENDANT STIPULATE TO FAMILY CODE SECTION 6211 AND PENAL CODE SECTION 1203.097
